strings:
<voice_0x01001739><se_low>King Trode: Ah! There you are, <hero>!
Just in the nick of time.
I knew I could depend on you.

<voice_0x0100173A><se_low>King Trode: You have to take Medea and escape from here
at once!
<voice_0x0100173B><se_low>King Trode: I can't possibly let that awful Prince Charmless marry my beautiful Medea.

<voice_0x0100173C><se_low>King Trode: My country's honour matters not one jot compared to her happiness.
Please, take her to safety!
